38K9*Interfaces 3|1r6 4r8 4|233e15
X 5 i-c.ads
30K20*C 3|1w17 4r19 5|598e17
99F9*double<long_float> 3|8r25 8r40 8r55 13r30 13r45 13r60 18r30 18r45 18r60
. 23r28 23r43 23r58 30r30 30r45 30r60 35r33 35r48 40r31 40r46 45r31 45r46
